    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263260/extras/7437e4f0937b21f47a3153067fb55d40.poster.avif?t=1761324495\" width=960 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263260/extras/7437e4f0937b21f47a3153067fb55d40.webm?t=1761324495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263260/extras/7437e4f0937b21f47a3153067fb55d40.mp4?t=1761324495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你扮演的是被困在轮椅上的凡妮莎，她试图逃离腐朽城市乌罗科一家即将倒塌的医院——在这里，当地的神话和扭曲的记忆交织成现实。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263260/extras/3cb0f3a855b889a5e430bf7cb3da5f13.poster.avif?t=1761324495\" width=960 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263260/extras/3cb0f3a855b889a5e430bf7cb3da5f13.webm?t=1761324495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263260/extras/3cb0f3a855b889a5e430bf7cb3da5f13.mp4?t=1761324495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏采用经典的坦克式操控方式，并经过重新设计，以传达轮椅的重量和精准度。每一次转弯、遇到的障碍以及反应迟缓都成为游戏体验的一部分——这并非限制，而是一种恐惧机制。挑战关乎身体、情感和深层心理层面。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263260/extras/95c9b90e7b1631d0df2ebe175dd5f24a.poster.avif?t=1761324495\" width=960 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263260/extras/95c9b90e7b1631d0df2ebe175dd5f24a.webm?t=1761324495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263260/extras/95c9b90e7b1631d0df2ebe175dd5f24a.mp4?t=1761324495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>凡妮莎需要解开谜题和秘密才能前进。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263260/extras/e3c5be490618b96fe851a3e41fb60082.poster.avif?t=1761324495\" width=960 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263260/extras/e3c5be490618b96fe851a3e41fb60082.webm?t=1761324495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263260/extras/e3c5be490618b96fe851a3e41fb60082.mp4?t=1761324495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>凡妮莎在黑暗的走廊中探索，她发现了武器和稀缺的资源，有限的库存迫使她不得不在防御和生存之间做出艰难的抉择。<br>萦绕在鳞状上空的实体灵感源自日本民间传说和传统戏剧，它们缓慢的姿态、变形的面具以及仪式性的动作，与能剧和歌舞伎相呼应——这两种艺术形式都沉浸于内疚、悔恨和精神上的越轨。<br><br>在挣扎求生的过程中，凡妮莎发现了记忆、记录和符号的碎片，并开始思考自己在这场悲剧中扮演的角色。<br>她是鳞状诅咒的受害者，还是诅咒崩塌的原因？",
